# fstrent_tasks_v2 System Overview

Whenever you use this rule, start your message with the following:

"Accessing fstrent_tasks_v2 system overview..."

The fstrent_tasks_v2 system is a comprehensive task management framework built on individual, specialized rules that work together to provide structured project development.

## Core Task Management Rules
- **`tasks.mdc`** - Primary task management with YAML schema and lifecycle
- **`expand.mdc`** - Task complexity assessment and breakdown logic
- **`bug_tracking.mdc`** - Bug identification and resolution tracking
- **`design_fixes.mdc`** - Retroactive documentation for fixes
- **`documentation_templates.mdc`** - Standardized documentation templates

## Planning & Scope Management
- **`plans.mdc`** - Product Requirements Document (PRD) creation
- **`planning_questionnaire.mdc`** - Requirements gathering framework
- **`scope_clarification.mdc`** - Scope validation and assumption checking
- **`anti_scope_creep.mdc`** - Over-engineering prevention (Core Innovation)

## Context & Memory System
- **`context_management.mdc`** - Project context awareness and task alignment
- **`memory.mdc`** - Historical task archival and knowledge preservation
- **`memory_consultation_triggers.mdc`** - Automatic memory activation
- **`context_optimization.mdc`** - Context efficiency monitoring

## Tool Integration & Workflow
- **`tool_awareness.mdc`** - Comprehensive MCP tool integration, task-tool mapping, and tool-first approach
- **`rule_activation.mdc`** - Advanced rule automation

## System Organization
- **`file_organization.mdc`** - Template vs working directory management (Critical)
- **`file_tracking.mdc`** - Project structure documentation
- **`workflow_diagrams.mdc`** - Visual workflow generation
- **`architecture_visualization.mdc`** - System visualization

## Quality & Process Management
- **`performance.mdc`** - Comprehensive performance analytics, metrics collection, and bottleneck analysis
- **`continuous_improvement.mdc`** - System evolution
- **`rule_improvements.mdc`** - Rule effectiveness analysis

## Optional Features
- **`sprint_planning.mdc`** - Iteration planning
- **`methodology_integration.mdc`** - Modern development practices
- **`rule_activation_tests.mdc`** - Rule testing framework (Optional)

## Directory Structure
```
.fstrent_tasks_v2/
├── tasks/                # Active task files
├── plans/               # PRDs and planning
├── memory/              # Historical archives
├── TASKS.md             # Master task checklist
├── PROJECT_CONTEXT.md   # Project mission
├── SUBSYSTEMS.md        # Component registry
└── FILE_REGISTRY.md     # File documentation
```

## Essential Rules for Basic Operation
1. `tasks.mdc` - Core task management
2. `file_organization.mdc` - Proper file handling
3. `context_management.mdc` - Project alignment
4. `memory.mdc` - Knowledge preservation

## Recommended Additions
